    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the support thing, but it feels so clinical. like trying to fix a broken lightbulb when the electricity is just gone. it's not just a mood or being sad... it's more like the essence of me, the thing that made life worth living, is just extinct. how do you find \"tools\" for something that isn't there anymore?",
